issue.title: Script setup
issue.body:
Moved all jupyter notebook logic into respective files.

Specifically:
## Servers
- `initialize_microstrategy_data.py` does not need to be run anymore, and has already been run once to populate database on MicroStrategy's end.
- `server.py` will run and wait, listening for new data to push up to MicroStrategy
- When `initialize_microstrategy_data.py` is run, two config files are saved in `data/` to hold the IDs of tables, etc.

## Data Generation
- `data/generate_data.py` will generate data biased slightly towards productivity occurring more in private spaces

## Machine learning
- `train.py` and `pred.py` respectively train and test a deep neural network

## TODO: (these are general TODO's, not just for this PR)
- When a new task is entered, update server + also predict what will happen?
- Visualize live?
- Figure out which visualizations to use
- How to push data to Rust server, if necessary?
- how to achieve MVP
- calculate which environmental factors are most important to the user (PCA)
- visualize above
